	   <tr><td colspan=2>Unfortunatly at level 12 you're hardly a rogue yet. Just a tank without Kick.&nbsp;&nbsp;:-(  <br><br>How do other tanks at your level deal with it?  Usually, its strength in numbers kind of deal.  Get with a group and stick with it.  Soloing at your level on a PK server is a bad thing.  Ambushes happen.  Get in cozy with a guild.  Use Hide and Sneak a lot.  Not every caster can see invis.  Even with all that you are still young.  At lower levels casters have the clear advantage.  Once you start getting over 20 the balance shifts.  BTW, if the mage goes out of line of site try using Evade.  Sometimes it drops their targeting.  Of course Evade only works as well as your Hide skill.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
