	   <tr><td colspan=2>The Sleeper has nothing at all to do with the rogue epic.&nbsp;&nbsp;Your friend maybe referring to Primal weapons.  The Sleeper is awoken only after all four warders in Sleepers Tomb are killed.  The Sleeper then awakes and causes havoc.  The status of the Sleeper varies from server to server.  Drinal, for one, is Sleeper free and I hope it remains that way for some time.<br><br>If you want more information on the rogue epic, this is the best and most thorough walkthrough.<br><br><a href="http://matt.waggoner.com/ragebringer.html" target=_new>http://matt.waggoner.com/ragebringer.html</a><br>&nbsp;<br>Dadiella 55th Lvl ROG Drinal<br><a href="http://www.unconquered.org" target=_new>http://www.unconquered.org</a><br></td></tr>
