	   <tr><td colspan=2>I would say get your strength up to about 75ish so you can carry stuff, and pump the rest into agility and dexterity.&nbsp;&nbsp;Agility adds to your AC and will affect how often you are hit, dexterity affects how often you will attack and hit, and it will help your skill levels go up faster.  Remember, a rogue is all about being quick and having style, not about trying to take out the MOB in three hits. <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
