	   <tr><td colspan=2>One other point I forgot:&nbsp;&nbsp;You can PP willowisps. Lord knows where they keep their pockets. Good low level coin.  If you have a magic weapon (or 2) and you are around level 13 you can fight them solo - carefully.  Even if you can't find a PC buyer for them selling the lightstones and greater lightstones to a vendor is decent loot.  <br><br>Fading Shadow Rapier is a good newbie weapon.  Not expensive. Not magic. But 6 dmg 22 dly is nothing to sneeze at.  If you know anyone hunting Tower of Frozen Shadow in Icelad Ocean have them pick one up for you.<br><br>You can pick pocket the giant mushroom things (reishis ?) in Luclin, too.  No coin but lots of free food.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
