	   <tr><td colspan=2>Money from pickpocketing does not get split with your group.&nbsp;&nbsp;It comes directly from the cash the group would get off the mob.  So if you pickpocket too much the mob will be left with only 1 piece of each type of coin he was carrying.<br>  Say you pickpocket 3 gold, 2 silver,6 copper over a fight thus picking clean Orc_Cent01.  When looted it will have 1 gold, 1 silver, 1 copper.  If you do this a lot your group will get suspicious.<br><br>Remember a good rogue never gets caught.<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Dadiella 55th Lvl ROG Drinal<br><a href="http://www.unconquered.org" target=_new>http://www.unconquered.org</a><br></td></tr>
