	   <tr><td colspan=2>Things to remember as a rogue, first off YOU ARE NOT A TANK!!! yes you do dmg better than a tank but you dont have the armor. If the mob even starts to agro you back away to let the tank take the hits, if you dont you are not being a good rogue and will soon be a dead one. If you want pull but I dont recommend it, the reason being is you have no way of making the agro leave you like the monk does and your hps arent as hi as a tank so pull if you want but I dont. As you get into higher lvls you need friends that trust you so dont pick pockets to much just enough to get a little more money than everone else, but not enough to be noticeable. Sneak and hide LEARN IT it will save youre life!! Things to remember if things get out of hand run before the tank dies not after, youre a rogue let the tank and the casters die get the hell out of the area and then drag there corpse's for them. Im now 30 lvl and have only died 3 times from my own stupid mistakes so enjoy:)&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br>Ceilironheart<br><br>44 rogue<br>19 sk<br>18 necro<br>17 druid<br>14 ranger<br>14 shammy<br>14 wizzy<br>5&nbsp;&nbsp;bard</td></tr>
