	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well I'm not sure if there's a way to port there. I believe you can get a port to the Great Divide if you have the key for it which is somewhere in the Great Divide.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you can get a port to Iceclad, it wouldn't be bad.  Although the journey is still quite far.  If you can't get a port, go to North Ro and wait at the docks.  Then take that raft, it'll lead you to the desert island on Iceclad.  When you get to the island, go to the other side of it and wait for the boat.  That boat will take you to the real part of Iceclad.  Afterwards the journey to EW is pretty far and can be dangerous so once you get there, ask for help.  It's still hard for me to explain it at times.<br>&nbsp;<br>Formerly Ishkur D`Macbain<br>Now...Ishkur Leroux<br>Teir'Dal Dobluth<br><br>"So what if I stabbed him in the back.&nbsp;&nbsp;His back was to me!"</td></tr>
